dct_title_s: New Milford, Bergen County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: "February 1923." Includes location map, key, streets and specials index, and text. "5827." North oriented towards upper right. Historic Maps copy includes sheets 1, 4 and 6 of New Milford, N.J. series; sheets 2-3, showing River Edge Manor section, sheet 5, showing Peetzburg section, and sheet 7, showing New Bridge section, foldered separately.
